ProMED-mail <promed@promedmail.org>

[In 2004, there was a _Corynebacterium_ that caused the YEP to
succumb to various ailments and illnesses. I am sure if the YEPT is
involved, they have requested testing for the various corynebacteria.
- Mod.TG]
